     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS</b></p><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS\"> </a><a name=\"hcIMMZD2DTRotavirusVS\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 22 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20less|20than|206|20weeks-41\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageislessthan6weeks-41\">Client's age is less than 6 weeks-41</a></td><td>Client's age is less than 6 weeks</td><td><div><p>'Today's date – \"Date of birth\" &lt; 6 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client|20is|20not|20due|20for|20rotavirus|20vaccination-48\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Clientisnotdueforrotavirusvaccination-48\">Client is not due for rotavirus vaccination-48</a></td><td>Client is not due for rotavirus vaccination</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Not due\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-No|20rotavirus|20primary|20series|20doses|20were|20administered-118\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Norotavirusprimaryseriesdoseswereadministered-118\">No rotavirus primary series doses were administered-118</a></td><td>No rotavirus primary series doses were administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rotavirus vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 0</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20between|206|20weeks|20and|2024|20months-52\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageisbetween6weeksand24months-52\">Client's age is between 6 weeks and 24 months-52</a></td><td>Client's age is between 6 weeks and 24 months</td><td><div><p>6 weeks ≤ Today's date – \"Date of birth\" &lt; 24 months</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-No|20live|20vaccine|20was|20administered|20in|20the|20last|204|20weeks-92\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Nolivevaccinewasadministeredinthelast4weeks-92\">No live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks-92</a></td><td>No live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date - latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Live vaccine\" = TRUE) ≥ 4 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client|20is|20due|20for|20rotavirus|20vaccination-44\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Clientisdueforrotavirusvaccination-44\">Client is due for rotavirus vaccination-44</a></td><td>Client is due for rotavirus vaccination</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Due\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Live|20vaccine|20was|20administered|20in|20the|20last|204|20weeks-92\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Livevaccinewasadministeredinthelast4weeks-92\">Live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks-92</a></td><td>Live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date - latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Live vaccine\" = TRUE) &lt; 4 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-One|20rotavirus|20primary|20series|20dose|20was|20administered-118\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Onerotavirusprimaryseriesdosewasadministered-118\">One rotavirus primary series dose was administered-118</a></td><td>One rotavirus primary series dose was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rotavirus vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 1</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Two|20rotavirus|20primary|20series|20doses|20were|20administered-118\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Tworotavirusprimaryseriesdoseswereadministered-118\">Two rotavirus primary series doses were administered-118</a></td><td>Two rotavirus primary series doses were administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rotavirus vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 2</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20between|206|20months|20and|2024|20months-52\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageisbetween6monthsand24months-52\">Client's age is between 6 months and 24 months-52</a></td><td>Client's age is between 6 months and 24 months</td><td><div><p>6 weeks ≤ Today's date – \"Date of birth\" ≤ 24 months</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-The|20series|20administered|20to|20the|20client|20is|20a|20mixed|20series|20or|20a|20series|20with|20unknown|20vaccine|20products-169\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Theseriesadministeredtotheclientisamixedseriesoraserieswithunknownvaccineproducts-169\">The series administered to the client is a mixed series or a series with unknown vaccine products-169</a></td><td>The series administered to the client is a mixed series or a series with unknown vaccine products</td><td><div><p>\"Vaccine brand\" (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rotavirus vaccines\" AND \"Dose number\" = 1) ≠ \"Vaccine brand\" (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rotavirus vaccines\" AND \"Dose number\" = 2)</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Live|20vaccines|20was|20administered|20in|20the|20last|204|20weeks-92\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Livevaccineswasadministeredinthelast4weeks-92\">Live vaccines was administered in the last 4 weeks-92</a></td><td>Live vaccines was administered in the last 4 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date - latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Live vaccine\" = TRUE) &lt; 4 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-No|20live|20vaccine|20was|20administered|20in|20last|204|20weeks-92\"> </a>